@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lbyhgu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.26 * v2 + 0.29)) - 0.23)
    tmp = wp.exp(v2)
    v0 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.66 * v0 + 0.37)) / (tmp / wp.cos(v2 + 0.52)))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v1 + 0.39) + 0.79))
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.cos(tmp + 0.48) / 0.50))
    v0 = wp.cos(v0)
    data[tid] = v0
